name: Jacky Bird
description:
WARNING: This game contains a lot of swear words. 

Welcome to Jacky Bird, a Flappy Bird x Jacksepticeye fan game! You play as Sam, trying to pass through his septic tanks. Why? No one knows! Share your high score in the comments to see who's the bigger BOSS and leave your valued feedback in the comments too!

This is my first solo (and 2D) game. Hopefully you like it!
